qada-wal-qadr","tag-provision-al-rizq","tag-punishment-al-uqubah","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-2Bi","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":10010,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/25\/qadr-dua-repel-divine-decree\/","url_meta":{"origin":10000,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication repels the divine decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing repels the divine decree but supplication, and nothing increases life span but righteousness.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2139 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u00a0Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0631\u064f\u062f\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20569,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/04\/11\/ask-allah-benefit-knowledge\/","url_meta":{"origin":10000,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ilm: Ask Allah for beneficial knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAsk Allah for beneficial knowledge and seek refuge in Allah from knowledge without benefit.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3843 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0633\u064e\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e \u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064b\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/dua-good-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":10000,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: I ask for Your every decree to be good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught her among the comprehensive supplications, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for Your every decree upon me to be good.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3846 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &